(56, 'Good Brain, Bad Brain: Drug Origins', 'Explore our past, present and future understanding of drugs with this free course. Where do drugs come from? How do theyÂ work?', 'This course is designed for anyone who has ever wondered how the drugs in their medicine cabinet were found in the first place and how they ended up as pills in a bottle.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/good-brain-bad-brain-drugs', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2389597.mp4', '2015-11-02', 2, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/30/94/regular_3094e11c-a724-4785-8780-58eb71aed537.jpg', 'Health & Psychology', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Birmingham', '2015-11-04 00:00:57'),
(57, 'Why Do We Age? The Molecular Mechanisms of Ageing', 'Why do we age? Is there a limit to human lifespan? Can we prolong our lives? Find out with this free onlineÂ course.', 'The âwhyâ and âhowâ of ageing has puzzled mankind ever since it questioned its place in the universe. However, it was only after infectious diseases became more controlled and reliable food supplies became generally available, that the rapid increase of the average lifespan made science turn its attention to study longevity and ageing.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/ageing', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3155756.mp4', '2015-11-02', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/42/2a/regular_422a2468-5da5-4fe4-85d9-bd78671b980c.jpg', 'Health & Psychology', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Groningen', '2015-11-04 00:00:58'),
(58, 'What is a Mind?', 'Explore the most pertinent scientific and philosophical concepts for understanding our own minds with this free onlineÂ course', 'This free online course will bring together learners and practitioners interested in how the mind works. It aims to build bridges between traditionally antagonistic approaches to understanding the mind.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/what-is-a-mind', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2817852.mp4', '2015-11-02', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/8a/dd/regular_8addb4ba-36d2-4d3c-a3d6-156bacd6690d.jpg', 'Health & Psychology', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Cape Town', '2015-11-04 00:00:58'),
(59, 'Improving Healthcare Through Clinical Research', 'Find out how medical treatments are discovered, tested and evaluated, to improve healthcare for all, on this free onlineÂ course.', 'Everything we do in healthcare - every tablet thatâs prescribed, every treatment thatâs given and every test thatâs performed - has to be first discovered and then thoroughly evaluated before it can be put into practice.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/clinical-research', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5394540.mp4', '2015-11-02', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/a8/e8/regular_a8e878c7-6b58-4e07-9895-ae0403ee7540.jpg', 'Health & Psychology', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Leeds', '2015-11-04 00:00:59'),
(60, 'The Mind is Flat: the Shocking Shallowness of Human Psychology', 'Make better personal and professional decisions, considering the psychological dimension to choices, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'What are the forces shaping human behaviour? How do we think and decide? This course, from Professor Nick Chater and Warwick Business School, explores the origins of human rationality and irrationality.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/the-mind-is-flat', '', '2015-11-09', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/12/3e/regular_123ecc58-cdac-4e5f-84b0-64a2964fcfdf.jpg', 'Health & Psychology', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Warwick', '2015-11-04 00:00:59'),
(61, 'Global Blindness: Planning and Managing Eye Care Services', 'Understand global blindness and how to plan effective eye care with this free online course for healthÂ professionals', 'Around the world, 285 million people are blind or visually impaired. 75% of this is avoidable and 90% is in low- and middle-income countries.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/global-blindness', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2956886.mp4', '2015-11-09', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/a3/af/regular_a3af1913-e926-4f89-a9b1-93b7911f7212.jpg', 'Health & Psychology', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'London School of Hygiene & Tropical Medicine', '2015-11-04 00:01:00'),
(62, 'The Genomics Era: the Future of Genetics in Medicine', 'Learn about the growing role of genomics in healthcare, for patient diagnoses and treatment, with this free onlineÂ course', 'This free online course will provide healthcare professionals with a basic grounding in genomic medicine. It will introduce you to the new genomic technologies that are revolutionising medicine and will, in time, provide the mainstay of patient diagnosis, treatment and disease prevention.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/the-genomics-era', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3533489.mp4', '2015-11-09', 5, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/8c/a3/regular_8ca34745-2d02-450b-8b70-b0c635368251.jpg', 'Health & Psychology', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'St Georges, University of London', '2015-11-04 00:01:01'),
(63, 'Measuring and Valuing Health', 'Learn how Patient Reported Outcome Measures and Quality Adjusted Life Years can compare treatments and inform healthcareÂ spending.', 'Healthcare systems around the world are increasingly under pressure to fund drugs, treatments and other healthcare interventions. No-one has the money or resources to provide them all, so how do we decide which ones to fund?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/valuing-health', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2389556.mp4', '2015-11-23', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/73/ff/regular_73ffffe7-2825-48fa-a20d-06136a97690f.jpg', 'Health & Psychology', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Sheffield', '2015-11-04 00:01:02'),
(64, 'Bioprinting: 3D Printing Body Parts', 'Discover how biomaterials and 3D printing collide, to create revolutionary, bioprinted body parts, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'You may be aware of 3D printing or have seen low-cost 3D printers, which can create plastic toys, replicas and objects of your own design. But did you know that 3D printing is also enabling life-saving and transforming medical procedures, which were unthinkable a few years ago?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/bioprinting', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4894894.mp4', '2015-11-23', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/e6/3f/regular_e63f6908-c6bc-4bc2-9059-d18064cac286.jpg', 'Health & Psychology', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Australian Institute for Innovative Materials, University of Wollongong ', '2015-11-04 00:01:02'),
(65, 'Clinical Supervision with Confidence', 'This course is designed to enhance the supervision skills of clinical and educational supervisors of traineeÂ doctors.', 'Supervise medical students and trainees effectively with this free online course, ideal for clinical and educational supervisors.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/clinical-supervision-with-confidence', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2770835.mp4', '2015-11-30', 2, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/13/16/regular_1316832d-7559-4531-b7f1-86742825ad34.jpg', 'Health & Psychology', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'UEA (University of East Anglia)', '2015-11-04 00:01:03'),
(66, 'Social Media in Healthcare: Opportunities and Challenges', 'Understand how social media is used in healthcare, to improve communication and information sharing, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'Social media has emerged as a new channel for both seeking information, and for creating and exchanging user-generated content among peers.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/social-media-in-healthcare', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5435393.mp4', '2015-11-30', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/e4/96/regular_e4961de7-feb1-455e-8114-c9471a3027f9.jpg', 'Health & Psychology', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Taipei Medical University', '2015-11-04 00:01:04'),
(67, 'Cancer in the 21st Century: the Genomic Revolution', 'Discover how genetics is revolutionising the detection and treatment of cancer, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'Cancer Research UK estimates that 1 in 2 people in the UK will be diagnosed with cancer during their lifetime. It is a disease that impacts on most peopleâs lives at some stage. So understanding cancer, and the development of new treatments, is of intrinsic interest to us all.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/cancer-and-the-genomic-revolution', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2958909.mp4', '2016-01-11', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/90/6f/regular_906f023f-dbe3-40ee-a8f5-2feb04c56828.jpg', 'Health & Psychology', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Glasgow', '2015-11-04 00:01:05'),
(68, 'Heart Health: a Beginners Guide to Cardiovascular Disease', 'Learn more about how your heart works, the causes of heart disease and how to keep your heart healthy with this free onlineÂ course', 'Your heart beats around 100,000 times a day, pumping blood around your body to deliver oxygen and nutrients, while taking away waste products.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/heart-health', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3123756.mp4', '2016-01-11', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/d4/fb/regular_d4fbef68-f45c-4b02-a1f4-a69d2a49f599.jpg', 'Health & Psychology', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Reading', '2015-11-04 00:01:05');
