(103, 'Understanding Drugs and Addiction', 'How do addictions develop? How are they best treated and prevented? Explore these key questions with this free onlineÂ course.', 'We are all touched by addiction â personally, within our circle of family and friends, and within our community. Addiction and its related harms can be crippling for those affected and the people around them.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/understanding-drugs-and-addiction', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2378628.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/1f/e2/regular_1fe271ce-ad9f-4bc4-85e0-d61816b21ca0.jpg', 'Health & Psychology', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Kings College London', '2015-11-04 00:01:29'),
