(110, 'World War 1: Lessons and Legacy of the Great War', 'Learn how the Allies defeat the Germans in World War 1, how the memory arose that the war was futile, and why this view isÂ untrue.', 'What is your understanding of World War I? Brave men led to their deaths by stupid officers? A war of trenches, mud and barbed wire in which there was no victor?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/ww1-lessons-legacy', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5356990.mp4', '2016-02-08', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/e1/4a/regular_e14ae70f-bd1a-47d8-b50d-adc5a53d0c61.jpg', 'History', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'UNSW Australia', '2015-11-04 00:01:35'),
(111, 'Military Ethics: An Introduction', 'We explore the ethical responsibilities that weigh on military professionals, who are âmanagers ofÂ violenceâ.', 'Military professionals are unusual in having the use of lethal force as a central, defining feature of their role, and unique in the level of force that they are authorized to use. This fact places a considerable ethical weight on military practitioners as well as the civilian decision-makers who authorize military missions.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/military-ethics', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5387660.mp4', '2016-02-29', 7, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/f2/02/regular_f2020743-f023-4d3a-bac1-fafa5907d58f.jpg', 'History', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'UNSW Australia', '2015-11-04 00:01:36'),
(112, 'World War 1: Changing Faces of Heroism', 'Learn how the war moved us away from traditional views of heroism and created new kinds of heroes andÂ heroines.', 'Did World War 1 make heroism meaningless or was it the conflict that gave it the most meaning? Weâve designed this course in partnership with the BBC to help you explore, discuss and challenge the ways in which World War 1 heroism has been remembered. Our experts will take you through the changing British, French and German views of heroism and discuss important similarities and differences.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/ww1-heroism', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3053661.mp4', '2015-10-26', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/40/b5/regular_40b5ca70-dc9c-4f4f-8a13-c75f40ba818d.jpg', 'History', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Leeds', '2015-11-04 00:01:37'),
(113, 'World War 1: A History in 100 Stories', 'Change the way you see World War 1 as you explore stories of hope, suffering and loss from newly released historicalÂ archives.', 'The Gallipoli Campaign was Australia and New Zealandâs first major military engagement of World War 1. The Anzacs went on to fight in Palestine, Egypt and the Western Front and suffered one of the highest casualty rates of any allied army.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/ww1-stories', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2377019.mp4', '2015-10-12', 5, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/42/6c/regular_426c9a51-9278-47d3-b64f-408dfe3d2e88.jpg', 'History', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Monash University', '2015-11-04 00:01:38'),
