(122, 'Superpowers of the Ancient World: the Near East', 'Experience the worldâs first international age, 3,500 years ago in the ancient Near East, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'Over four weeks, this free online course explores four ancient Near-Eastern cultures and how they interacted with each other 3,500 years ago.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/superpowers-near-east', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4115194.mp4', '0000-00-00', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/33/8c/regular_338c724e-a5c0-4318-a826-0d253678383d.jpg', 'History', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Liverpool', '2015-11-04 00:01:45'),
(123, 'Wellington and the Battle of Waterloo', 'Mark the bicentenary of the Battle of Waterloo in 2015 and explore the Duke of Wellingtonâs archive with this free onlineÂ course.', 'The Battle of Waterloo was one of the key events of nineteenth-century history, but why was it fought, who was involved and what were consequences? This free online course will answer these questions, marking the 200th anniversary of Waterloo on 18 June 2015.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/wellington-and-waterloo', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3618045.mp4', '0000-00-00', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/b7/09/regular_b70934ab-3aa0-49d0-bef4-65a71b896686.jpg', 'History', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Southampton', '2015-11-04 00:01:46'),
(124, 'World War 1: Aviation Comes of Age', 'Investigate how the white heat of innovation in World War 1 shaped the history of humanÂ flight.', 'Investigate how the early days of aviation gripped the imagination of the general public, galvanised industry and excited far-sighted members of the military, with this free online course from the University of Birminghamâs Centre for War Studies.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/ww1-aviation', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3340918.mp4', '0000-00-00', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/09/4b/regular_094bbaf9-ed37-4ba6-8bf0-5f83f47471e9.jpg', 'History', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Birmingham', '2015-11-04 00:01:46'),
(125, 'World War 1: Paris 1919 - A New World Order?', 'This course reassesses the legacy of the Paris Peace Conference (1919) and how it sought to create a new worldÂ order.', 'The Paris Peace Conference of 1919 ended a Great War, but it also designed the post-war future. In 1919, world leaders assembled in Paris redrew the map of the world, partitioned and created countries, and ushered in a new era of international relations. The naivety of the peace-makers of 1919 has been justly criticised. However, in setting up a permanent âworld organisationâ, the League of Nations, they changed the management of world affairs forever.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/ww1-new-world-order', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2196589.mp4', '0000-00-00', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/23/7e/regular_237e6c99-3f52-4853-96e0-bafa0e3dfdd1.jpg', 'History', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Glasgow', '2015-11-04 00:01:47'),
(126, 'Introduction to Dutch', 'Learn to speak, write and understand basic Dutch, with this free, three-week, introductory foreign languageÂ course.', 'Are you planning to visit, or work or study in the Netherlands soon? This free online course is perfect if you have little or no prior knowledge of Dutch, but would like to master the fundamentals in order to survive life in the Low Countries.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/dutch', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2912826.mp4', '2015-11-02', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/29/24/regular_2924bac4-50c7-4855-80b9-32894b3635ef.jpg', 'Culture & Language', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Groningen', '2015-11-04 00:01:50'),
(127, 'Intercultural Communication', 'Learn to appreciate, adjust to, and work or study in different cultures, with this free online intercultural communicationÂ course.', 'Whether youâre engaging in business across borders or cultural regions, meeting other people through international travel, working in a diverse, global organisation or studying abroad, you can benefit from a better understanding of intercultural communication.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/intercultural-communication', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5346186.mp4', '2015-11-09', 5, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/73/7e/regular_737e6fa1-bed3-4711-b089-cc21677a10e8.jpg', 'Culture & Language', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Shanghai International Studies University (SISU)', '2015-11-04 00:01:51'),
(128, 'Exploring English: Magna Carta', 'Improve your English language skills while exploring the Magna Carta - the 800-year-old "great charter" that shaped theÂ world.', 'How did a peace treaty signed by an English king in 1215 become such an important symbol of liberty and human rights around the world?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/explore-english-magna-carta', '', '2015-11-30', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/9b/3f/regular_9b3f3036-7191-4f53-8aea-db43abe85b28.jpg', 'Culture & Language', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'British Council', '2015-11-04 00:01:51'),
(129, 'Exploring English: Shakespeare', 'Improve your English language skills by looking at the life and works of William Shakespeare and his enduringÂ popularity.', 'This free online course will look at the life and works of William Shakespeare and take you from his Birthplace in Stratford-upon-Avon to the Globe Theatre in London, from where he secured his central place in English literature.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/explore-english-shakespeare', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5517695.mp4', '2016-01-11', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/df/30/regular_df30152c-3fd2-4f96-a151-a39fcead4da3.jpg', 'Culture & Language', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'British Council', '2015-11-04 00:01:52'),
(130, 'A Beginners Guide to Writing in English for University Study', 'Learn how to use English for study at university or college and develop your writing skills, vocabulary andÂ grammar.', 'If youâre interested in studying at university or college in an English-speaking country, youâll need to learn how to write using academic English. Academic writing can be very different from other types of English writing you may have done in the past. We have developed this course to help you learn the basics of academic writing and develop your English skills for study in the UK, US, Australia or other countries where English is used.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/english-for-study', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2840424.mp4', '2016-01-18', 5, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/a7/4c/regular_a74c84a4-b484-4372-ae31-4db7c100529b.jpg', 'Culture & Language', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Reading', '2015-11-04 00:01:53'),
(131, 'Exploring English: Language and Culture', 'This course for learners of English looks at British culture and examines English in use to help you improve your languageÂ skills.', 'This course is for people who are learning English and who are interested in finding out more about British culture and improving their English language skills.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/explore-english-language-culture', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3031601.mp4', '2015-10-19', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/ab/54/regular_ab54c18c-fe97-4b06-aee1-7ef578503e9f.jpg', 'Culture & Language', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'British Council', '2015-11-04 00:01:53'),
(132, 'Understanding Language: Learning and Teaching', 'An introduction to some key concepts in the effective teaching and learning ofÂ languages.', 'What is language? How do we learn meaning in a new language? What is easy and hard about learning another language? And what is the best way to teach other languages?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/understanding-language', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2497255.mp4', '2015-10-12', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/8d/f5/regular_8df536e7-bcbf-45eb-8599-d8aa0da56616.jpg', 'Culture & Language', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Southampton', '2015-11-04 00:01:54'),
(133, 'Cultural Studies and Modern Languages: an Introduction', 'Explore the culture, language and national identity of eight countries through their books, images, slogans andÂ monuments', 'Are you interested in other countries? Do you want to study and understand other cultures? This free online course will take you on a journey through a number of periods from the medieval to the modern day, from Russia to Europe and all the way to Latin America.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/cultural-studies', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2428991.mp4', '2015-09-28', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/b5/c7/regular_b5c7c300-3189-4c96-ae66-597a6192c138.jpg', 'Culture & Language', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Bristol', '2015-11-04 00:01:55');
