(135, 'The European Discovery of China', 'Explore Chinese history through the eyes of Western travellers, discoverers and missionaries, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'This free online course focuses on when and how the West first approached China. We will explore the influence that the discovery of China exerted on late medieval and early modern European minds.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/european-discovery-china', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3990564.mp4', '0000-00-00', 8, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/71/04/regular_7104226d-9edf-44b2-8bb4-956bebc969aa.jpg', 'Culture & Language', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Pompeu Fabra University Barcelona', '2015-11-04 00:01:57'),
(136, 'Dyslexia and Foreign Language Teaching', 'Gain practical tools and theoretical insights to help dyslexic students learn second languages, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'Dyslexia affects 10-15% of the population. Dyslexic students are often either exempted from the study of additional languages or they underperform in foreign language classes.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/dyslexia', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2555787.mp4', '0000-00-00', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/67/6c/regular_676cb58f-d5b5-4b13-9aa1-7b8bb2477e99.jpg', 'Culture & Language', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Lancaster University', '2015-11-04 00:01:57'),
(137, 'Muslims in Britain: Changes and Challenges', 'Develop your understanding of Muslims and their faith through an exploration of communities inÂ Britain.', 'Islam is the second largest religion in the world today and dominates much of the current geopolitical discourse. People are increasingly bombarded by dramatic and at times disturbing headlines. Yet general knowledge of Muslims and their faith can be poor. There is consequently a need for a balanced and well-informed understanding of the current debates around this internationally significant topic.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/muslims-in-britain', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2296530.mp4', '0000-00-00', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/d8/1a/regular_d81a635c-cda9-41d4-b9aa-8b7d997970dc.jpg', 'Culture & Language', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Cardiff University', '2015-11-04 00:01:58'),
(138, 'Professional Practices for English Language Teaching', 'A free online continuing professional development (CPD) course for people who are teaching English as a foreignÂ language.', 'This free online course is for English language teachers around the world. It will help you develop the skills and practices you need for your continuing professional development (CPD).', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/english-language-teaching', '', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/a9/cf/regular_a9cf89ec-1531-4cfe-839c-a23cbabfdea2.jpg', 'Culture & Language', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'British Council', '2015-11-04 00:01:58'),
(139, 'Understanding IELTS: Techniques for English Language Tests', 'Improve your English and prepare for tests, such as IELTS reading, writing, speaking and listening, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'Anyone thinking about taking an English language test, such as IELTS, will find this course particularly useful, but all English language learners will benefit from the tips and advice given in the course.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/understanding-ielts', '', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/a2/a5/regular_a2a50e02-4364-4ef7-9353-32ce4fda2f09.jpg', 'Culture & Language', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'British Council', '2015-11-04 00:01:59'),
(140, 'Antiquities Trafficking and Art Crime', 'Delve into the seedy underbelly of the art world, looking at smuggling, theft, fakes, and fraud, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'The devastation caused by the trafficking of illicit antiquities and the theft of art has gained widespread public attention in recent years.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/art-crime', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5348091.mp4', '2016-02-01', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/a0/fd/regular_a0fd2545-9657-4fa4-9769-f4f910c9d9b7.jpg', 'Law', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Glasgow', '2015-11-04 00:02:01'),
(141, 'Crime, Justice and Society', 'Explore the role of the state and criminal justice interventions in producing safe and justÂ societies', 'Crime and criminal justice are vast and fascinating issues that highlight the complexity of defining and solving social problems.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/crime-justice-society', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4928778.mp4', '2015-10-12', 7, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/a4/08/regular_a4085e9b-8156-4c36-b135-378813639661.jpg', 'Law', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Sheffield', '2015-11-04 00:02:02'),
(142, 'Forensic Psychology: Witness Investigation', 'Discover how psychology can help obtain evidence from eyewitnesses in police investigations and prevent miscarriages ofÂ justice.', 'Explore how your own mind works, and discover how the limitations of the human brain can lead to major miscarriages of justice.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/forensic-psychology', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2340401.mp4', '2015-09-14', 8, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/bd/09/regular_bd0923f5-3b95-4cf4-b0b9-297a9706d19d.jpg', 'Law', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The Open University', '2015-11-04 00:02:03'),
(143, 'Forensic Science and Criminal Justice', 'Learn how police use science in criminal investigations and its role in the criminal justice system with this free onlineÂ course.', 'Over the past two decades, the criminal justice system has been dramatically affected by technological advances in scientific contributions to the law. The most influential developments have been in the area of DNA profiling, and its forensic applications for both identifying perpetrators and exonerating the innocent.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/forensic-crim-justice', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2493477.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/f7/63/regular_f76375a2-d1f5-4625-b706-1b5b5e3a67f9.jpg', 'Law', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Leicester', '2015-11-04 00:02:04'),
(144, 'Exploring English: Shakespeare', 'Improve your English language skills by looking at the life and works of William Shakespeare and his enduringÂ popularity.', 'This free online course will look at the life and works of William Shakespeare and take you from his Birthplace in Stratford-upon-Avon to the Globe Theatre in London, from where he secured his central place in English literature.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/explore-english-shakespeare', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5517695.mp4', '2016-01-11', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/df/30/regular_df30152c-3fd2-4f96-a151-a39fcead4da3.jpg', 'Literature & Writing', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'British Council', '2015-11-04 00:02:05'),
(145, 'Start Writing Fiction', 'This hands-on course helps you to get started with your own fiction writing, focusing on the central skill of creatingÂ characters.', 'Start Writing Fiction focuses on a skill which is central to the writing of all stories and novels â creating characters.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/start-writing-fiction', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2648205.mp4', '2016-01-18', 8, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/51/db/regular_51dbd3e2-84fa-4356-ad38-6b76738b6b03.jpg', 'Literature & Writing', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The Open University', '2015-11-04 00:02:06'),
(146, 'An Introduction to Screenwriting', 'This free online course explores the key concepts and fundamental principles involved in the process ofÂ screenwriting.', 'Screenplays form the starting point for most dramatic films, the essential work from which all other filmmaking flows. All of the tender romance, terrifying action and memorable lines begin at the screenwriterâs desk. This free online course will introduce you to the basic elements and key concepts behind a professional screenplay.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/screenwriting', '', '2016-02-29', 2, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/d2/70/regular_d270e847-b243-4ba7-ade2-a3b4a551e420.jpg', 'Literature & Writing', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'UEA (University of East Anglia)', '2015-11-04 00:02:06'),
(147, 'World War 1: Changing Faces of Heroism', 'Learn how the war moved us away from traditional views of heroism and created new kinds of heroes andÂ heroines.', 'Did World War 1 make heroism meaningless or was it the conflict that gave it the most meaning? Weâve designed this course in partnership with the BBC to help you explore, discuss and challenge the ways in which World War 1 heroism has been remembered. Our experts will take you through the changing British, French and German views of heroism and discuss important similarities and differences.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/ww1-heroism', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3053661.mp4', '2015-10-26', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/40/b5/regular_40b5ca70-dc9c-4f4f-8a13-c75f40ba818d.jpg', 'Literature & Writing', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Leeds', '2015-11-04 00:02:07'),
(148, 'Hans Christian Andersenâs Fairy Tales', 'Explore the fairy tale world of HC Andersen - the inspiration behind The Little Mermaid and Frozen - with this free onlineÂ course.', 'This free online course will introduce you to some of Hans Christian Andersenâs most popular fairy tales, share the story of the writer himself, and discuss his cross-cultural importance today, as the inspiration behind many popular books and movies.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/hans-christian-andersens-fairy-tales', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4397780.mp4', '2015-10-19', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/84/b6/regular_84b6a8b0-d253-4b29-982a-97e3f608c85c.jpg', 'Literature & Writing', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Hans Christian Andersen Centre', '2015-11-04 00:02:07'),
(149, 'Cultural Studies and Modern Languages: an Introduction', 'Explore the culture, language and national identity of eight countries through their books, images, slogans andÂ monuments', 'Are you interested in other countries? Do you want to study and understand other cultures? This free online course will take you on a journey through a number of periods from the medieval to the modern day, from Russia to Europe and all the way to Latin America.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/cultural-studies', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2428991.mp4', '2015-10-12', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/b5/c7/regular_b5c7c300-3189-4c96-ae66-597a6192c138.jpg', 'Literature & Writing', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Bristol', '2015-11-04 00:02:08'),
