(200, 'Childhood in the Digital Age', 'Delve into the lives of children and discuss the potential benefits and limitations of technology in theirÂ lives.', 'Are you a technology optimist or a technology pessimist?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/childhood-in-the-digital-age', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4530272.mp4', '0000-00-00', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/14/f8/regular_14f8f7d0-c6ec-4d94-a99c-acff489aeb38.jpg', 'Programming & IT', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The Open University', '2015-11-04 00:02:44'),
(201, 'Community Journalism: Digital and Social Media', 'Gain practical skills and insights into hyperlocal journalism, and use digital and social media to create your own newsÂ website.', 'Community journalism is a growing area of interest for professional journalists, academics and the wider public. The decline of local newspapers and radio stations, coupled with the low cost of publishing online, means there are more community journalism and hyperlocal websites being launched everyday.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/community-journalism', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2358128.mp4', '0000-00-00', 5, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/d3/54/regular_d3548457-a375-456b-8ecc-7533e9050fca.jpg', 'Programming & IT', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Cardiff University', '2015-11-04 00:02:46'),
(202, 'Creative Coding', 'Use computer programming as a creative discipline to generate sounds, images, animations and more, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'Learning to program is no longer just for computer specialists and software developers. People from many different backgrounds now want to understand the basics of programming, because itâs both fun and an increasingly valuable skill.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/creative-coding', 'http://view.vzaar.com/1569932.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/8e/98/regular_8e98b3b7-689e-457a-95ac-c1523d7d5242.jpg', 'Programming & IT', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Monash University', '2015-11-04 00:02:47'),
(203, 'Digital Storytelling: Filmmaking for the Web', 'Combine theory and practice to tell powerful stories through film online. Unleash your potential in this free onlineÂ course.', 'The University of Birmingham, the BBC Academy and Creative Skillset have combined forces, to create this four-week, free online course.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/digital-storytelling', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4315019.mp4', '0000-00-00', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/9a/b5/regular_9ab51686-7c98-4e16-ba4b-d59af4d71ce1.jpg', 'Programming & IT', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Birmingham', '2015-11-04 00:02:48'),
(204, 'Teaching Computing', 'A free online course for primary and secondary school teachers who are tackling the Computing curriculum inÂ England.', 'This free online course aims to help teachers in primary schools and at Key Stage 3, who are delivering the Computing curriculum, which was introduced to schools in England in September 2014.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/teaching-computing', '', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/d2/c5/regular_d2c51ff2-0c67-41aa-ab9c-10e9c1835f4e.jpg', 'Programming & IT', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'UEA (University of East Anglia)', '2015-11-04 00:02:49'),
(205, 'Sustainability, Society and You', 'Join us for an introduction to the major global issue of sustainability and discover how you can have a real impact on ourÂ future.', 'Sustainability is one of the big global issues of our time. It is crucial that we all play our part in protecting our world for current and future generations. This course provides you with the knowledge and skills to do this by investigating sustainability from multiple angles and exploring what small steps you can take to have a real impact upon all our futures.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/sustainability-society-and-you', '', '2015-11-02', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/fa/de/regular_fade2622-3ae1-4ff2-83db-af529fc98553.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Nottingham', '2015-11-04 00:02:50'),
(206, 'Tackling the Global Food Crisis: Supply Chain Integrity', 'The challenges for food security in tracing and detecting food contamination whether it be by accident or as a result ofÂ fraud.', 'Humanity faces a considerable problem in maintaining and enhancing food supplies on a global basis, whilst improving our wellbeing in both the developing and developed world. Obesity and other growing problems related to dietary excess pose huge economic and health implications in the developed world.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/global-food-crisis', 'http://view.vzaar.com/1987197.mp4', '2015-11-02', 5, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/09/05/regular_09056b37-f7ba-43cb-92ff-bfffcbe948ae.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Queens University Belfast', '2015-11-04 00:02:51'),
(207, 'Tackling the Global Food Crisis: Sustainable Agrifood Systems', 'This course looks at food insecurity and the challenges to be overcome in order to maintain healthy and sustainable foodÂ supplies.', 'This is the second course in a two-part series by Queenâs University Belfast looking at issues concerning the maintenance and enhancement of global food supplies, whilst improving human wellbeing in the developed and developing world.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/agrifood', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2089358.mp4', '2016-01-11', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/58/5f/regular_585f12a2-9455-4cf3-b969-3e04243a1934.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Queens University Belfast', '2015-11-04 00:02:52'),
(208, 'Africa: Sustainable Development for All?', 'Learn what progress Africa has made towards inclusive development and consider challenges post-2015 in this free onlineÂ course.', 'Africa as a continent is rich in natural resources and minerals and has increasing rates of wealth in some countries. The course will explore why there continues to be many sub-Saharan African countries which perform poorly on development indicators for reducing poverty, hunger and unemployment and improving maternal health and access to quality reproductive health services.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/africa-sustainable-development', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3920380.mp4', '2016-01-25', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/32/6a/regular_326a81ea-0cc3-4bde-9ddf-a78ccbeea382.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Aberdeen', '2015-11-04 00:02:52'),
(209, 'Understanding Public Financial Management: How Is Your Money Spent?', 'How do governments acquire and spend public money? Take a fresh look at public financial management with this free onlineÂ course.', 'What went wrong in Greeceâs handling of its public debt? How does a city government like Detroit go from prosperity to bankruptcy? And how could the looting, theft and corruption in Malawiâs âcashgateâ have been avoided?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/public-financial-management', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5441427.mp4', '2016-01-25', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/ef/12/regular_ef1250d1-3017-48da-b50d-d032a15e5029.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'SOAS, University of London', '2015-11-04 00:02:53'),
(210, 'Military Ethics: An Introduction', 'We explore the ethical responsibilities that weigh on military professionals, who are âmanagers ofÂ violenceâ.', 'Military professionals are unusual in having the use of lethal force as a central, defining feature of their role, and unique in the level of force that they are authorized to use. This fact places a considerable ethical weight on military practitioners as well as the civilian decision-makers who authorize military missions.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/military-ethics', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5387660.mp4', '2016-02-29', 7, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/f2/02/regular_f2020743-f023-4d3a-bac1-fafa5907d58f.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'UNSW Australia', '2015-11-04 00:02:53'),
(211, 'Scotland and Wales Vote 2016: Understanding the Devolved Elections', 'This course wil examine the issues, ideas and institutions involved in the Scottish Parliament and Welsh AssemblyÂ elections.', '2016 is an exciting year for elections in the United Kingdom. Towards the end of the year we might have a referendum on the UKâs EU membership, but we definitely know that there will be elections to the Scottish Parliament and Welsh Assembly in May. Both of these institutions have a significant impact on peopleâs lives in Scotland and Wales: they control big public policy issues like health, education and transport.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/scottish-welsh-elections16', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5435747.mp4', '2016-04-11', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/b5/25/regular_b525867d-1a7e-4f70-bda6-760e3fc5a516.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Edinburgh', '2015-11-04 00:02:54'),
(212, 'Crime, Justice and Society', 'Explore the role of the state and criminal justice interventions in producing safe and justÂ societies', 'Crime and criminal justice are vast and fascinating issues that highlight the complexity of defining and solving social problems.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/crime-justice-society', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4928778.mp4', '2015-10-12', 7, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/a4/08/regular_a4085e9b-8156-4c36-b135-378813639661.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Sheffield', '2015-11-04 00:02:55'),
(213, 'Religion and Conflict', 'Understand and analyze the role of religion in conflicts and peacebuilding in present-day societies, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'Many conflicts in the world today are framed in terms of religion, but there is much discussion and confusion concerning the precise role religion plays in these conflicts. According to some, conflict and violence are inherent to religion. Others claim that religion is only the guise under which social, economic or political conflicts are fought out. The first step to solving religiously framed conflicts is understanding the role of religion in them, and that is what this free online course is about.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/religion-and-conflict', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3022180.mp4', '2015-10-05', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/d7/ef/regular_d7ef63d4-5ee9-409f-9b5f-be27016bc9eb.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Groningen', '2015-11-04 00:02:56'),
(214, 'Causes of War', 'What causes armed conflict in the world today? Examine current thinking on this critical question with this free onlineÂ course.', 'This free online course will introduce you to current thinking on the causes of armed conflict in the world today. It looks at a range of modern and historical conflicts and draws on a variety of theories and approaches. It will appeal to anyone with an interest in world affairs.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/causes-of-war', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2641095.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/a0/69/regular_a069122d-914e-4328-8fcd-704562070123.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Kings College London', '2015-11-04 00:02:56'),
(215, 'Challenging Wealth and Income Inequality', 'Explore the concerns about rising generational and economic inequality in developed countries, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'From religious leaders to heads of state, everyone is talking about economic inequality. What form can such inequality take in different countries? What impact does it have on society? And why should it matter to you?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/inequalities-in-personal-finance', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2763907.mp4', '0000-00-00', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/c6/8f/regular_c68fc17f-f2b2-4b0d-b9d3-2ef55bb681d9.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The Open University', '2015-11-04 00:02:57'),
(216, 'Cooperation in the Contemporary World: Unlocking International Politics', 'Why do we cooperate? How can we achieve more lasting cooperation? This course explores the puzzle in international politicsÂ today.', 'As world leaders seek to find a solution to crises in Syria and Ukraine; economists try to reinvigorate stalling global financial markets; and a range of actors gather to find a consensus on climate change, there has never been a better time to understand the puzzle of cooperation.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/cooperation-in-the-contemporary-world', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4149980.mp4', '0000-00-00', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/1c/c6/regular_1cc604f0-636e-425d-80a9-34ae7880a164.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Birmingham', '2015-11-04 00:02:58'),
(217, 'Environmental Justice', 'Understand how environmental change affects people, and how we can work together for justice in environmentalÂ management.', 'The world faces challenging environmental problems. They are challenging because different people typically contribute differently to environmental change, and because its effects will be felt differently by different people in different places.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/environmental-justice', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2428282.mp4', '0000-00-00', 10, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/b2/83/regular_b283c88b-3644-499d-b965-cef376be50cd.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'UEA (University of East Anglia)', '2015-11-04 00:02:58'),
(218, 'From State Control to Remote Control: Warfare in the 21st Century', 'Explore the impact and ethics of using drones, special ops units and private security firms, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'States are increasingly using remote control methods, such as drones, private military companies and special operations units, to engage in activities that were traditionally performed by their conventional armed forces.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/remote-control-warfare', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2662019.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/d8/17/regular_d817f134-8706-4769-a704-12400797fbfc.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Bath', '2015-11-04 00:02:59'),
(219, 'Global Food Security: Addressing the Challenge', 'How will we feed an extra two billion people by the middle of thisÂ century?', 'In this course, we introduce the issue of food security and explore some of the different ways in which it has been described both in research and in practice and consider key concerns for the future.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/food-security', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2550056.mp4', '0000-00-00', 8, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/74/1a/regular_741a7f06-e579-4f08-8bc0-a2efb60c4a7a.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Lancaster University', '2015-11-04 00:03:00'),
(220, 'Identity, Conflict and Public Space', 'Explore how people use public spaces around the world to protest and express their identity, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'In ethnic and political conflicts around the world, public spaces are used by diverse groups of people, to express their identity and protest about their beliefs:', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/identity-conflict-and-public-space', 'http://view.vzaar.com/1401981.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/14/19/regular_141937f4-9e01-430f-b96d-d16c9868e28c.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Queens University Belfast', '2015-11-04 00:03:00'),
(221, 'Lips and Teeth: Korea and China in Modern Times', 'Explore the historical evolution of China and the Korean Peninsula and discover the implications forÂ today.', 'As countries across Asia - and the globe - wrestle with the impact of Chinaâs rise, nowhere are the opportunities and threats of a wealthy and powerful China felt more keenly than next door, on the Korean Peninsula.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/korea-and-china', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2419110.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/60/5e/regular_605e0239-009a-451d-aa14-57eee58b3259.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Yonsei University', '2015-11-04 00:03:01'),
(222, 'Modern Korean History: Liberation, War and Nuclear Ambitions', 'Explore the unique and untold history of North and South Korea - from 1945 to the present - with this free onlineÂ course.', 'The contemporary history of the Korean peninsula has been a tumultuous tale of decolonization, war and rapid economic development. Both North and South Korea has had an immense impact on the world stage and today many wonder why this region of East Asia appears so frequently in the international news.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/modern-korean-history', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2372067.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/ff/51/regular_ff5143af-a195-45ae-9e42-aff3857da80e.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Yonsei University', '2015-11-04 00:03:02'),
(223, 'Propaganda and Ideology in Everyday Life', 'Find out how propaganda is used to instil political ideologies and its impact on our daily lives, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'This free online course explores the building blocks of our political views: freedom, community, place, justice and choice.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/propaganda', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2801553.mp4', '0000-00-00', 5, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/ef/23/regular_ef2351cc-cde8-4ed0-9801-4bfc380e0930.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Nottingham', '2015-11-04 00:03:03'),
(224, 'Shale Gas and Fracking: the Politics and Science', 'Hear from all sides of the fracking debate with this free online course. Understand what shale gas is and why it dividesÂ opinion.', 'Shale gas is seen by many as a cheap, clean and plentiful source of energy; a low-carbon âgame changerâ helping us meet the worldâs rapidly growing demands for energy and offering greater energy security. Its rapid rise has not been without controversy, however. Earth tremors, surface and groundwater contamination, and the effects of fracking on human and animal health are all high profile concerns.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/shale-gas', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2317839.mp4', '0000-00-00', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/3c/ac/regular_3caca682-b4ac-4240-8621-d58a9c0ac586.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Nottingham', '2015-11-04 00:03:03'),
(225, 'Superpowers of the Ancient World: the Near East', 'Experience the worldâs first international age, 3,500 years ago in the ancient Near East, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'Over four weeks, this free online course explores four ancient Near-Eastern cultures and how they interacted with each other 3,500 years ago.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/superpowers-near-east', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4115194.mp4', '0000-00-00', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/33/8c/regular_338c724e-a5c0-4318-a826-0d253678383d.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Liverpool', '2015-11-04 00:03:04'),
(226, 'The Lottery of Birth', 'Birth is a lottery. Where, when and to whom you are born and the society into which you are born will influence your lifeÂ chances.', 'This free online course will look at both the big picture of the âlottery of birthâ and the smaller, human stories. You will examine the inequalities of birth, particularly being born rich or poor and being born female or male.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/lottery-of-birth', '', '0000-00-00', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/04/33/regular_04332853-0e02-4bcb-ba23-c4a2275ac789.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The Open University', '2015-11-04 00:03:05'),
(227, 'What Works: Promising Practices in International Development', 'Explore promising strategies in international aid related to agriculture, public health, governance, and povertyÂ reduction.', 'The history of international development is a complicated mixture of hopeful altruism and difficult reality. The media often paint development aid as wasteful spending, leaving the public wondering if any intervention can ever work. Yet can the case be made for a more optimistic outlook on international development?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/what-works', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2402606.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/17/fc/regular_17fc7ab1-9d5f-4463-be05-efedf4120f31.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Oslo', '2015-11-04 00:03:05'),
(228, 'World War 1: Paris 1919 - A New World Order?', 'This course reassesses the legacy of the Paris Peace Conference (1919) and how it sought to create a new worldÂ order.', 'The Paris Peace Conference of 1919 ended a Great War, but it also designed the post-war future. In 1919, world leaders assembled in Paris redrew the map of the world, partitioned and created countries, and ushered in a new era of international relations. The naivety of the peace-makers of 1919 has been justly criticised. However, in setting up a permanent âworld organisationâ, the League of Nations, they changed the management of world affairs forever.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/ww1-new-world-order', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2196589.mp4', '0000-00-00', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/23/7e/regular_237e6c99-3f52-4853-96e0-bafa0e3dfdd1.jpg', '', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Glasgow', '2015-11-04 00:03:05'),
