(234, 'Our Changing Climate: Past, Present and Future', 'Find out more about the climate of the past and how climate change can present a number of risks andÂ opportunities.', 'Since early humans first moved out of Africa, the worldâs climate has had a continual impact on our history. Now, the climate itself is being shaped by civilisation.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/our-changing-climate', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5039268.mp4', '2015-11-09', 5, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/36/b7/regular_36b75c03-07cd-4c6f-b0d8-93118da74a70.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Reading', '2015-11-04 00:03:14'),
