(243, 'Smart Cities', 'Explore the role of technology and data in cities, and learn how you can participate in the creation of smartÂ cities.', 'Cities are incubators of innovation and opportunities but they also face great challenges such as rapid urbanisation, climate change and inequality. How can smart cities address these challenges and become more resilient? And what role will people play in the design and planning of our smart cities?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/smart-cities', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4320132.mp4', '2016-01-18', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/c8/67/regular_c8674e50-15bc-424f-85ff-055fff956043.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The Open University', '2015-11-04 00:03:22'),
