(247, 'Numeracy Skills for Employability and the Workplace', 'Improve your mathematical confidence and gain the skills to pass employersâ numeracy tests with this free onlineÂ course.', 'In our highly technical world numeracy skills, particularly the ability to interpret data, are becoming increasingly important and are highly sought after by employers.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/numeracy-skills', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3100937.mp4', '2015-10-19', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/ef/ee/regular_efeeb9bf-a129-455c-a1f0-f4727d81bf2b.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Loughborough University', '2015-11-04 00:03:24'),
(248, 'Moons', 'Explore the many moons of our Solar System. Find out what makes them special. Should we send humans to our MoonÂ again?', 'There are lots of moons in our Solar System. The Earth is the only planet with just a single moon. Some moons are bigger than ours; many are much smaller. There are even tiny moons orbiting some of the asteroids. Some have ongoing volcanic eruptions; others are dead, heavily cratered lumps. One has rivers and lakes of liquid methane. Our own Moon has resources that could help open the Solar System for future exploration. A small handful of moons have conditions below their surfaces where primitive life might exist.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/moons', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2096693.mp4', '2015-10-19', 8, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/45/58/regular_45589460-fec1-4b42-96d9-ecd89c0a4e13.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The Open University', '2015-11-04 00:03:25'),
(249, 'Data to Insight: An Introduction to Data Analysis', 'This course is a hands-on introduction to statistical data analysis that emphasises fundamental concepts and practicalÂ skills.', 'Organisations around the world are collecting more data than ever. They are talking about big data, data science, business intelligence, analytics, data mining and data visualisation, and thereâs an urgent need for people with the data skills to understand, interpret and communicate this information.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/data-to-insight', 'http://view.vzaar.com/1644667.mp4', '2015-10-19', 8, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/e5/09/regular_e50950a6-e653-4933-9443-6a25900440be.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Auckland', '2015-11-04 00:03:25'),
