(256, 'Causes of Climate Change', 'Understand the physical processes behind climate variations in the past, present and future, with this free onlineÂ course', 'This free online course provides the basis for understanding the underlying physical processes governing climate variations in the past, present and future.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/causes-of-climate-change', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4147256.mp4', '0000-00-00', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/a1/84/regular_a184ac4b-f773-4ba7-87bb-fb9a23b1792c.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Bergen', '2015-11-04 00:03:30'),
(257, 'Climate Change: Challenges and Solutions', 'This course aims to explain the science of climate change, the risks it poses and the solutions available to reduce thoseÂ risks.', 'The course is aimed at the level of students entering university, and seeks to provide an inter-disciplinary introduction to what is a broad field. It engages a number of experts from the University of Exeter and a number of partner organisations.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/climate-change-challenges-and-solutions', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2136990.mp4', '0000-00-00', 8, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/cb/71/regular_cb71114d-b163-4486-908d-20dadfde623e.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Exeter', '2015-11-04 00:03:30'),
(258, 'Decision Making in a Complex and Uncertain World', 'This course will teach you the first principles of complexity, uncertainty and how to make decisions in a complexÂ world.', 'Leaders must be able to act in a complex world and under uncertainty. This course is a first step to develop yourself into one of the futureâs key decision makers or to enhance your decision-making skills.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/complexity-and-uncertainty', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2182037.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/f6/28/regular_f6280438-ac86-4f67-9ff2-6d5bdda3e9ea.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Groningen', '2015-11-04 00:03:31'),
(259, 'Discover Dentistry', 'An entertaining and illuminating course for everyone to explore the impact dentistry has on ourÂ lives.', 'How important is a smile? Ever wondered what all those letters and numbers a dentist calls out during your check-up mean? How are broken teeth fixed, or how dentures are made? Join Dr Christopher Stokes on a learning journey to explore the dental profession and the impact dentistry has on all our lives.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/discover-dentistry', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3951348.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/c9/0a/regular_c90a27ee-232d-4bd6-bc98-aa66ec60d481.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Sheffield', '2015-11-04 00:03:31'),
(260, 'Dysphagia: Swallowing Difficulties and Medicines', 'This course will enhance the knowledge of any person involved in the administration of medicines to patients withÂ dysphagia.', 'The course offers an opportunity to network with other learners and with the creators of the course through discussions, graphs and social networking features and to share knowledge with other learners and professionals. By completing this online course participants will be able to describe:', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/dysphagia', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3261218.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/16/6c/regular_166c19c9-7eab-48da-b7b8-c21e383c1f58.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'UEA (University of East Anglia)', '2015-11-04 00:03:32'),
(261, 'Ebola in Context: Understanding Transmission, Response and Control', 'How has the Ebola outbreak become a humanitarian emergency? Learn about the science behind theÂ crisis.', 'In 2014, Ebola went from a scarcely known virus to the subject of daily news reports. The epidemic in West Africa has quickly surpassed all previous outbreaks, to become an unprecedented humanitarian crisis.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/ebola-in-context', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2714612.mp4', '0000-00-00', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/46/1b/regular_461b7c93-fba6-4151-a140-cbdf9422c2bf.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'London School of Hygiene & Tropical Medicine', '2015-11-04 00:03:32'),
(262, 'Ebola: Symptoms, History and Origins', 'Learn about Ebola, its symptoms, where it came from and what the current outbreak has taught us, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'In December 2013, the largest outbreak of Ebola virus disease (EVD) that the world has ever seen, began in West Africa - a region of the continent that has historically been free of it.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/ebola', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3089045.mp4', '0000-00-00', 2, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/d9/5e/regular_d95ef0b5-c747-4815-bcde-26ebc3d0f87d.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Lancaster University', '2015-11-04 00:03:33'),
(263, 'Elements of Renewable Energy', 'Learn how sustainable energy from the Greek elements â Earth, Air, Fire and Water â can replace fossil fuels and nuclearÂ power.', 'In recent decades thereâs been increasing global concern about the sustainability of our use of fossil fuels and nuclear power, which has led to increased interest in more sustainable renewable energy sources.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/elements-renewable-energies', '', '0000-00-00', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/0e/e1/regular_0ee1deec-38ac-46df-82a5-4d4b0f0bad4c.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The Open University', '2015-11-04 00:03:34'),
(264, 'Exploring Anatomy: the Human Abdomen', 'Explore the anatomy of the human abdomen and understand its clinicalÂ importance.', 'This course introduces you to the human abdomen and explores its many complex structures. As the course progresses, the structure and function of important organs will be demonstrated, discussed and related to common surgical scenarios and current research. Each of the three weeks will focus on a specific area of the abdomen; starting at the surface you will then enter the abdomen and be able to detail the anatomy of numerous organs including the stomach and liver.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/anatomy', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2321495.mp4', '0000-00-00', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/0c/d4/regular_0cd42bec-6ea7-425f-9306-c84c455c8c6f.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Leeds', '2015-11-04 00:03:35');
INSERT INTO `course_data` (`id`, `title`, `short_desc`, `long_desc`, `course_link`, `video_link`, `start_date`, `course_length`, `course_image`, `category`, `site`, `course_fee`, `language`, `certificate`, `university`, `time_scraped`) VALUES
(265, 'Exploring Our Oceans', 'Explore the half of our world covered by deep ocean, and how our lives affect the hidden face of ourÂ planet.', 'The first astronauts to leave the Earthâs orbit saw our âblue planetâ for the first time. But what lies in the half of our world covered by water more than two miles deep? How are our everyday lives connected to the ocean depths, and what challenges and opportunities does this previously hidden realm hold for our future?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/exploring-our-oceans', '', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/d9/e6/regular_d9e61125-ca2d-4240-abba-751ca981345f.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Southampton', '2015-11-04 00:03:35'),
(266, 'Forensic Science and Criminal Justice', 'Learn how police use science in criminal investigations and its role in the criminal justice system with this free onlineÂ course.', 'Over the past two decades, the criminal justice system has been dramatically affected by technological advances in scientific contributions to the law. The most influential developments have been in the area of DNA profiling, and its forensic applications for both identifying perpetrators and exonerating the innocent.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/forensic-crim-justice', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2493477.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/f7/63/regular_f76375a2-d1f5-4625-b706-1b5b5e3a67f9.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Leicester', '2015-11-04 00:03:36'),
(267, 'Getting a Grip on Mathematical Symbolism', 'Want to be an engineer or scientist? Lack mathematical confidence? Learn to think mathematically and explore essentialÂ concepts.', 'This course is aimed at those who aspire to study science or engineering foundation courses at university level. It draws upon the experience of staff from the Mathematics Education Centre at Loughborough University - a centre that has specialised for many years in mathematics teaching and mathematics support for science and engineering students who find the transition to university mathematics particularly challenging.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/mathematical-symbolism', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2344107.mp4', '0000-00-00', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/95/49/regular_95497a58-f83d-4043-992d-1fea57d922ca.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Loughborough University', '2015-11-04 00:03:38'),
(268, 'Identifying the Dead: Forensic Science and Human Identification', 'Uncover a grave, examine remains and reveal the victimâs identity in this free online course, linked to a new Val McDermidÂ story.', 'The first step in any investigation involving a death is to determine the identity of the deceased. This free online course will take you on a journey through the world of forensic anthropology, unveiling the tools that will allow you to reveal that identity.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/identifying-the-dead', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4188357.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/9c/c5/regular_9cc5596f-9ebf-4c55-a426-0d2aee889f95.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Dundee', '2015-11-04 00:03:39'),
(269, 'Inside Cancer: How Genes Influence Cancer Development', 'Understand how genetics influence the development and spread of cancer, with this free, introductory onlineÂ course.', 'Cancer is a disease that affects around one-third of the human population, irrespective of nationality or ethnic origins. There are many types of cancer, but they all have one thing in common - they begin as rebel or mutant cells.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/inside-cancer', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2285126.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/17/73/regular_1773392a-c546-49f6-b52a-bee15ce2a57a.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Bath', '2015-11-04 00:03:40'),
(270, 'Introduction to Forensic Science', 'Methods & scientific underpinning of forensic science, from crime scene investigation to reporting evidential value within aÂ case.', 'The course addresses four major evidence types: drugs of abuse, DNA, firearms and impression evidence, and discusses these through the exploration of a case-based scenario presented across a six-week modular framework.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/introduction-to-forensic-science', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3055990.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/25/6b/regular_256bf98e-3ae2-4836-a7fb-350b393568f8.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Strathclyde', '2015-11-04 00:03:41'),
(271, 'Kitchen chemistry', 'Use your kitchen as a laboratory to learn about chemistry using everydayÂ chemicals.', 'The Kitchen Chemistry course is designed to explore some of the principles of chemistry. You will be encouraged to carry out your own experiments using materials that are often found in the home. If not they can be obtained from most supermarkets, pharmacies or hardware stores.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/kitchen-chemistry', 'http://view.vzaar.com/1472601.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/32/bf/regular_32bfe603-fb54-4557-8a38-c112feab03eb.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'UEA (University of East Anglia)', '2015-11-04 00:03:42'),
(272, 'Metabolomics: Understanding Metabolism in the 21st Century', 'Discover how metabolomics is revolutionising our understanding of metabolism with this free onlineÂ course.', 'Metabolomics is an emerging field that aims to measure the complement of metabolites (the intermediates and products of metabolism) in living organisms. The complement of metabolites in a biological system is known as the metabolome and represents the downstream effect of an organismâs genome and its interaction with the environment. Metabolomics has a wide application area across the medical and biological sciences and is attractive to both new and established scientists. In this course we will provide an introduction to metabolomics, explain why we want to study the metabolome and describe the current challenges in analysing the complement of metabolites in a biological system. We will describe the interdisciplinary approaches adopted in the metabolomics workflow and demonstrate how the combined efforts of scientistâs from different disciplines is advancing this exciting field. By the end of the course the learner will understand how metabolomics can revolutionise our understanding of metabolism.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/metabolomics', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4782792.mp4', '0000-00-00', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/e3/84/regular_e384a622-583e-4778-b412-78614e422023.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Birmingham', '2015-11-04 00:03:43'),
(273, 'Soils: Introducing the World Beneath Our Feet', 'Learn about soils, the variety of life they contain and how humans impact this fragile system, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'Soils are a vital part of our planetâs functioning, but all too often we take soils for granted. In this free online course, we introduce you to soils and explore the world beneath our feet.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/soils', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3693052.mp4', '0000-00-00', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/42/e6/regular_42e6e9b4-5a4f-43b4-bd68-ecd46f957777.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Lancaster University', '2015-11-04 00:03:44'),
(274, 'The Discovery of the Higgs Boson', 'Should we be excited about the Higgs boson? Find out more about particle physics and understanding theÂ universe.', 'The discovery of a new fundamental particle at the Large Hadron Collider (LHC), CERN is the latest step in a long quest seeking to answer one of physicsâ most enduring questions: why do particles have mass? The experimentsâ much anticipated success confirms predictions made decades earlier by Peter Higgs and others, and offers a glimpse into a universe of physics beyond the Standard Model.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/higgs', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2181886.mp4', '0000-00-00', 7, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/c3/08/regular_c308b27f-50ab-4d87-9d3d-c530c07f3a69.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Edinburgh', '2015-11-04 00:03:45'),
(275, 'The Science of Medicines', 'Learn the science behind how and why medicines work, and what can improve patients treatment, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'The worldâs growing population faces major health issues, and medicines are a primary pillar to effect better health. Learn about the science of key medicines used to manage heart disease, depression, diabetes, pain control and smoking cessation.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/the-science-of-medicines', '', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/a3/2d/regular_a32d14b8-c30d-4218-b151-b0a596206f68.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Monash University', '2015-11-04 00:03:46'),
(276, 'The Science of Nuclear Energy', 'Discover the science behind nuclear energy and its role in energy provision in the past, present andÂ future.', 'With the need to reduce carbon emissions around the world, the way we generate our power has to change and nuclear energy is back on the political agenda. But do you know your fission from your fusion? Would you like the knowledge to make an informed decision?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/the-science-of-nuclear-energy', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3933347.mp4', '0000-00-00', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/2c/51/regular_2c51f90d-2504-47bb-8816-c834b4e29b99.jpg', 'Maths, Science & Engineering', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The Open University', '2015-11-04 00:03:46'),
(277, 'Football: More than a Game', 'Explore the role of football in the world today - including finances, clubs, nations and rivalries - with this free onlineÂ course.', 'At the beginning of the twentieth century, football was the most popular game in the western world and has since grown to become a global spectacle.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/football', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3057075.mp4', '2016-01-25', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/90/2d/regular_902d0c48-095e-4919-81aa-4b8f4d3f198c.jpg', 'Leisure & Sports', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Edinburgh', '2015-11-04 00:03:47'),
(278, 'Exploring Play: The Importance of Play in Everyday Life', 'Understanding the nature and value of play through the course of our lives, across cultures andÂ communities.', 'Play your partâ¦ Play the foolâ¦ All work and no playâ¦ Childâs playâ¦ Fair playâ¦ Play a jokeâ¦ Play with fireâ¦', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/play', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5053351.mp4', '2015-10-19', 7, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/67/b9/regular_67b9b2fa-8b51-49bd-9327-005da7f4a2ef.jpg', 'Leisure & Sports', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Sheffield', '2015-11-04 00:03:48'),
(279, 'Blended Learning Essentials: Getting Started', 'A free course for the Vocational Education and Training sector to promote effective practice and pedagogy in blendedÂ learning.', 'If you are working in further education, skills training, vocational education, workplace learning, lifelong learning or adult education, this free online course is designed to help you understand the benefits of blended learning and how to make more effective use of technology to support your learners.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/blended-learning-getting-started', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5003250.mp4', '2015-11-02', 5, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/2d/f4/regular_2df4a5a6-f997-4bd1-80f4-b47ac4d22fcb.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Leeds', '2015-11-04 00:03:49'),
(280, 'How to Succeed at: Interviews', 'This free three week course provides the tools you need to succeed at interviews and land your dream job or courseÂ place.', 'This course will help you to succeed at interviews, whether you are applying for jobs or planning to study. Because being offered an interview can be quite daunting, weâve put together a set of materials to help you prepare and be successful on the day.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/interviews', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3030237.mp4', '2015-11-16', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/e1/6a/regular_e16aaa55-5f57-43f6-801f-cccc179f1e21.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Sheffield', '2015-11-04 00:03:50'),
(281, 'Get Started with Online Learning', 'This free online course will explain how you can study online without putting the rest of your life onÂ hold.', 'The internet is playing a bigger role in our lives, as we buy our groceries, manage our finances, share social experiences and otherwise live our lives online. But how many of us have considered studying online?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/online-learning', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4763094.mp4', '2016-01-04', 2, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/ce/19/regular_ce19db60-1224-442e-9df3-e38913259994.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The Open University', '2015-11-04 00:03:51'),
(282, 'A Beginners Guide to Writing in English for University Study', 'Learn how to use English for study at university or college and develop your writing skills, vocabulary andÂ grammar.', 'If youâre interested in studying at university or college in an English-speaking country, youâll need to learn how to write using academic English. Academic writing can be very different from other types of English writing you may have done in the past. We have developed this course to help you learn the basics of academic writing and develop your English skills for study in the UK, US, Australia or other countries where English is used.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/english-for-study', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2840424.mp4', '2016-01-18', 5, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/a7/4c/regular_a74c84a4-b484-4372-ae31-4db7c100529b.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Reading', '2015-11-04 00:03:53'),
(283, 'Preparing for University', 'This course will help develop the key skills required for a smooth transition toÂ university.', 'Higher education is about learning at a higher level: developing skills relating to critical thinking; holding a supported, substantive argument; analysing and using data or sources critically. These are university-level skills but you can work on the foundations of these skills before you get there. Such skills will also help in assessments such as A-levels and extended project work. They are also attributes that employers value in graduates.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/preparing-for-uni', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3053360.mp4', '2016-01-25', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/9a/f1/regular_9af1f97a-31b3-4d40-947e-22a28eed8370.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'UEA (University of East Anglia)', '2015-11-04 00:03:53'),
(284, 'Teaching Literacy Through Film', 'Learn how to use film in the classroom, teach literacy and improve both reading and writing skills, with this free onlineÂ course', 'Why use film to teach literacy? This free online course, led by film education experts from the British Film Institute (BFI) and film education charity Into Film, will examine the debate surrounding film as a vehicle for teaching literacy, alongside recent evidence demonstrating significant improvements in childrenâs reading and writing through use of film texts.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/teaching-literacy-through-film', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5531364.mp4', '2016-01-25', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/24/cf/regular_24cf4d7a-2552-4a69-862c-32c3c941ad99.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The British Film Institute (BFI)', '2015-11-04 00:03:54'),
(285, 'Academic Integrity: Values, Skills, Action', 'This course will explore academic integrity and how you can demonstrate it in your work, study and research atÂ university.', 'What is academic integrity? Why is it so important in academia? And how can you, as a student at university, achieve with integrity and honesty?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/academic-integrity', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2684892.mp4', '2016-02-01', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/e9/03/regular_e903f210-2e65-4bd9-bbd2-67e80e17a0d1.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Auckland', '2015-11-04 00:03:55'),
(286, 'Blended Learning Essentials: Embedding Practice', 'This is the second part of a course for the Vocational Education and Training sector to promote effective use of blendedÂ learning.', 'This is the second part of the Blended Learning Essentials course, which will build upon the content of the first part, covering issues such as learning from experience and tackling difficult challenges with the help of blended learning.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/blended-learning-embedding-practice', 'http://view.vzaar.com/5559266.mp4', '2016-02-01', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/29/04/regular_2904f7f4-b0e0-449b-a860-5a49bb2e5aed.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Leeds', '2015-11-04 00:03:55'),
(287, 'What is Character? Virtue Ethics in Education', 'Explore important questions about character education and how it contributes to individual and societalÂ flourishing.', 'Character education is increasingly being talked about by politicians, employers, teachers, parents and young people across the world. Can teaching virtues such as honesty, self-control, fairness, resilience and respect - which contribute to good character - be part of the solution to many of the challenges facing society today?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/what-is-character', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2159171.mp4', '2015-10-26', 2, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/b8/39/regular_b839d53f-5708-44c5-be0d-a7b7e421b9c9.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Birmingham', '2015-11-04 00:03:56'),
(288, 'How to Succeed at: Writing Applications', 'This free three week course will help you produce a perfect CV, application and online profile when applying for a job orÂ course.', 'This course will help you to write successful applications, whether you are applying for jobs or planning to study at university or college.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/writing-applications', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3030168.mp4', '2015-10-26', 3, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/fa/28/regular_fa284db2-d323-432d-8930-3ef8addefcb4.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Sheffield', '2015-11-04 00:03:56'),
(289, 'Understanding Language: Learning and Teaching', 'An introduction to some key concepts in the effective teaching and learning ofÂ languages.', 'What is language? How do we learn meaning in a new language? What is easy and hard about learning another language? And what is the best way to teach other languages?', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/understanding-language', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2497255.mp4', '2015-10-19', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/8d/f5/regular_8df536e7-bcbf-45eb-8599-d8aa0da56616.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Southampton', '2015-11-04 00:03:57'),
(290, 'Logical and Critical Thinking', 'Improve your logical and critical thinking skills in this free online course. Identify common obstacles to effectiveÂ thinking.', 'We are constantly being given reasons to do and believe things: to believe that we should buy a product, support a cause, accept a job, judge someone innocent or guilty, that fairness requires us to do some household chore, and so on. Assessing the reasons we are given to do or believe these things calls upon us to think critically and logically.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/logical-and-critical-thinking', 'http://view.vzaar.com/4129686.mp4', '2015-09-28', 8, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/a4/5e/regular_a45e1791-4619-4c75-a5eb-98ee33da42b1.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'The University of Auckland', '2015-11-04 00:03:58'),
(291, 'Preparing for University', 'This course will help develop the key skills required for a smooth transition toÂ university.', 'Higher education is about learning at a higher level: developing skills relating to critical thinking; holding a supported, substantive argument; analysing and using data or sources critically. These are university-level skills but you can work on the foundations of these skills before you get there. Such skills will also help in assessments such as A-levels and extended project work. They are also attributes that employers value in graduates.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/preparing-for-uni', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3053360.mp4', '2015-09-28', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/9a/f1/regular_9af1f97a-31b3-4d40-947e-22a28eed8370.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'UEA (University of East Anglia)', '2015-11-04 00:03:59'),
(292, 'Developing Your Research Project', 'Undertaking an Extended Project Qualification, IB extended essay or any other scholarly research? This guides youÂ step-by-step.', 'Curiosity is one of humanityâs most important characteristics. It has enabled us to make the unknown known, to break barriers and to shine a light on all aspects of life, from our day to day hobbies to the exploration of the stars. Our innate desire to explore is responsible for many of our proudest achievements. This course will help train you to harness your curiosity and use it to undertake your own research projects in a scholarly manner.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/research-project', 'http://view.vzaar.com/3028851.mp4', '2015-09-14', 8, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/09/ac/regular_09ac5f73-22ae-4186-a8e7-b74d9702f1ac.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Southampton', '2015-11-04 00:04:00'),
(293, 'Assessment for Learning in STEM Teaching', 'A free online course led by Dylan Wiliam and Christine Harrison, to help STEM teachers get to grips with Assessment forÂ Learning.', 'Assessment for Learning is a term thatâs widely used in education, but applied in ways that are variable in their effectiveness. This free online course - designed for STEM teachers in primary and secondary schools, and sixth form and further education (FE) colleges - will help you understand and use it more effectively.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/assessment-for-learning', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2428566.mp4', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/49/67/regular_49671185-1361-47f7-b320-5e36fe2a2883.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Leeds', '2015-11-04 00:04:01'),
(294, 'Dyslexia and Foreign Language Teaching', 'Gain practical tools and theoretical insights to help dyslexic students learn second languages, with this free onlineÂ course.', 'Dyslexia affects 10-15% of the population. Dyslexic students are often either exempted from the study of additional languages or they underperform in foreign language classes.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/dyslexia', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2555787.mp4', '0000-00-00', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/67/6c/regular_676cb58f-d5b5-4b13-9aa1-7b8bb2477e99.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'Lancaster University', '2015-11-04 00:04:01'),
(295, 'Professional Practices for English Language Teaching', 'A free online continuing professional development (CPD) course for people who are teaching English as a foreignÂ language.', 'This free online course is for English language teachers around the world. It will help you develop the skills and practices you need for your continuing professional development (CPD).', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/english-language-teaching', '', '0000-00-00', 6, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/a9/cf/regular_a9cf89ec-1531-4cfe-839c-a23cbabfdea2.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'British Council', '2015-11-04 00:04:02'),
(296, 'Study Skills for International Students', 'A course looking at key skills that international students need in order to be successful at a UKÂ university.', 'This course looks at some of the key skills that international students need in order to be successful at a UK university. It is special because of the way it has been produced. Our English language and study skills teachers at INTO UEA surveyed and interviewed students who had already successfully completed a course and progressed to study at the University. We asked them about the things that they had found most challenging when they started their university programme. This course has been developed as a result of what those international students told us, as well as the experience INTO UEA colleagues have in preparing international students for university study.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/study-skills-for-international-students', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2042029.mp4', '0000-00-00', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/af/29/regular_af29b508-568e-46c0-a9a7-019969ae2223.jpg', 'Studying & Teaching', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'UEA (University of East Anglia)', '2015-11-04 00:04:03'),
